OL,6,FSamantha Davis, the wife of Star Wars
OL,7,Fand Harry Potter actor Warwick Davis,
OL,8,Fhas died aged 53.
OL,10,FWarwick announced the news in a
OL,11,Fstatement shared to the BBC, revealing
OL,12,Fshe had died on March 24.
OL,14,FSamantha co-founded the dwarfism
OL,15,Fcharity Little People UK and featured
OL,16,Fin the final Harry Potter film,
OL,17,Falongside Warwick.
