OL,3,CActor Warwick Davis' wife Samantha
OL,4,Cdied aged 53
OL,6,F"Her passing has left a huge hole in
OL,7,Four lives as a family. I miss her
OL,8,Fhugs," Warwick said in the statement
OL,9,Fto the BBC.
OL,11,FHe added that she was his "most
OL,12,Ftrusted confidant and an ardent
OL,13,Fsupporter of everything I did in my
OL,14,Fcareer".
OL,16,FThe actor continued: "She was a unique
OL,17,Fcharacter, always seeing the sunny
OL,18,Fside of life she had a wicked sense of
OL,19,Fhumour and always laughed at my bad
OL,20,Fjokes."
