OL,3,CActor Warwick Davis' wife Samantha
OL,4,Cdied aged 53
OL,6,FThe couple met on the set of George
OL,7,FLucas's film Willow and married three
OL,8,Fyears later in 1991.
OL,10,FSamantha also played a goblin in Harry
OL,11,FPotter And The Deathly Hallows: Part 2
OL,12,Fwhile her husband played both
OL,13,FProfessor Flitwick and the goblin
OL,14,FGriphook in all eight films in the
OL,15,Ffranchise.
OL,17,FTheir two children together, Annabelle
OL,18,Fand Harrison, also paid tribute to
OL,19,Ftheir mother, saying: "Her love and
OL,20,Fhappiness carried us through our whole
OL,21,Flives"
