OL,6,FHe told the US outlet: "I think it
OL,7,Fbrings you closer together, or
OL,8,Fsomething like that. But it's an
OL,9,Fexperience I wouldn't wish on anyone.
OL,10,FIt's devastating."
OL,12,FA few years later they experienced
OL,13,Fmore heartbreak when Samantha had a
OL,14,Fmiscarriage with their second child.
OL,16,FThey later welcomed their daughter
OL,17,FAnnabelle and son Harrison, with
OL,18,FWarwick saying the couple loved their
OL,19,Fchildren "all that more because
OL,20,Fthey're here with us".
