OL,6,FAnnabelle, 27, has followed in her
OL,7,Fparents' acting footsteps, starring in
OL,8,FCBBC's The Dumping Ground and Channel
OL,9,F4 soap Hollyoaks.
OL,11,FWarwick starred as the titular hero
OL,12,FWillow Ufgood in the 1988 original
OL,13,Ffilm Willow and reprised the role for
OL,14,Fthe 2022 sequel.
OL,16,FHe also played several characters in
OL,17,Fthe Star Wars film series.
OL,19,FSamantha and Warwick co-founded Little
OL,20,FPeople UK in 2012 to help individuals
OL,21,Fwith dwarfism and their families.
